-- Yemen Court Sentences Al-Qaeda Bomb Maker to Death, Al Arabiya TV Reports
-- B y   I n a l   E r s a n
-- 2010-10-18T06:51:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-18/yemen-court-sentences-al-qaeda-bomb-maker-to-death-al-arabiya-tv-reports.html
A Yemeni court sentenced to death
Saleh al-Shawesh, identified as an al-Qaeda explosives expert,
Al Arabiya television reported today without giving further
details.  To contact the reporter on this story:
